{"tid":1027164,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"屌你老未 你班傻閪籃波撚真係好撚煩","createTime":"2019-02-18T15:30:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-18T19:39:50.000Z","uid":5190,"like":65,"dislike":39,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"edb551f906547e40fafce4e4a7dd3c20763ba8cd","tid":1027164,"uid":5190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T15:30:20.000Z","msg":"得啦知你係班小朋友為咗證明玩具唔係玩具而話足波係玩具啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n跑幾步又入波跑幾步又入波 成個場我十步跑撚晒 仲細撚過我屋企 唔通我平時係屋企行嚟行去又做緊運動？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n打下手仔又嗌foul 成個女人咁 又乜春搏盡無悔 懶係感性  屌你老母好撚嘔心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n係人都知籃球係玩具 原本都無乜人得閒理鳩你班傻閪 無啦啦又要係到嘈 嘈撚完又係柒嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />不如收收皮 繼續係室內冷氣地方行幾步路玩下籃波仔啦<br />\n<br />\n再唔係嘅咪成個弱智咁 幻想下自己係乜乜柒占咁 行行下街轉身射個三分波囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我係隔離我一定要拍撚晒手掌 再讚係射得好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b5e1a05af53319ccfb08fc11dec2362ce130508","tid":1027164,"uid":5190,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T15:32:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63c37f557f460e1b3d68fc05b71647ab28d51e67","tid":1027164,"uid":5190,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T15:34:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a22ebde8765a32351551f58b78aec0a